# 1.4.0

* Completely rewriting all graphs;
* Data live-displayed on the graph can be filtered (1/5/15 minutes old);
* Displayed battery level is more accurate;
* Removing deprecated dependencies and unused code.

# 1.3.0

* Reviewing entire application design.

# 1.2.1

* Application does not crash anymore if geolocation is not activated;
* User can define warning and danger thresholds for all PM categories;
* Notifications are automatically sent if current PM values exceed thresholds.